seller.description:
I am a self taught Fullstack software engineer (Web/Mobile/Software) who is having more than 6+ years of experience in the field. 

I also attained a Bachelor degree in Information Technology from University of Colombo School of Computing.

I am an expert in PHP, MySQL, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, Pixel Perfect design, Bootstrap, LESS, SASS, ReactJs, Responsive web design, Web development, Software development, Mobile app development, Shopify, WordPress, WooCommerce, Magento, Joomla and many more.

I'm passionate about technology and in my free time, I create electronic circuits and do experiments.
